Description: Famous street food in Mumbai is an Indian Street food made by stuffing deep fried potato fritters and served with spicy chutneys in side of Pav.
Served with spicy chole, crumbled kachori, yogurt, mint & tamarind chutney.
Savoury snack from the streets of Mumbai made with puffed rice, tossed with potatoes, onion, tomato & tangy chutneys.
